       Change Summary Explanation
       Funding: The FY 2026 request was reduced by $0.035 million for Advisory and Assistance Services to promote efficiencies and advance the policies of the
       Administration in alignment with Executive Order 14222, "Implementing the President's Department of Government Efficiency Cost Efficiency Initiative." The
       remaining reduction is due to rate adjustments.

       The FY 2026 request was reduced by $0.022 million for civilian personnel to optimize the workforce in compliance with Executive Order 14210, "Implementing the
       President's Department of Government Efficiency Workforce Optimization Initiative."

       Schedule: The MATI schedule has been extended to achieve additional USMC requirements. FY24 MATI/MUDLAN CONADD funding reprioritization allows
       inclusion of M3 Hybrid Communications and Next Gen BLOS (Island Wraith) which continues throughout FY25, ultimately extending the project into 1QFY26.




