Title: Defensive Cyber Operations - Cyber Analytics (PEO EIS)                                                                               24.565          26.100      27.927
Description: DCO Cyberspace Analytics Big Data Platform (BDP) is a scalable software-based, hardware agnostic capability
hosted in the cloud, called Gabriel Nimbus (GN). GN provides data indexing, user interfaces, and visualization tools accessible
