D. Acquisition Strategy
The DCO Information System Initial Capabilities Document (IS ICD) was approved on 19 December 2017 by the Army Requirements Oversight Council (AROC). DCO
programs are under an IT Box construct with five-year term (FY 2023-2027 approved on 31 August 2023) which aligns with current Requirements Definition Packages
(RDPs). IT Box establishes funding thresholds, by appropriation, for a program over the capability's projected lifecycle of five (5) years.



