CWAES: Conduct System Requirements Review, begin delivery of prototypes, commence developmental
testing.
NGRWH: Receive acquisition strategy approval, award prototype Other Transaction Authority (OTA) contracts,
receive prototypes, and begin evaluations for downselection to single vendor.
