       Schedule:

       Project Unit 2175/Tactical Air Electronic Warfare:
       Acquisition Milestones: ALQ-214 Adaptive Radar Countermeasures (ARC) Initial Operational Capability (IOC) removed due to funding constraints. ARC Build 2
       and Build 3 Deliveries added. Build 3 SW delivery reflects the final ARC SW build that will be provided in FY2026.
       Systems Development: DBD EMD Design Review 1 and 2 shifted from 3QFY24 and 4QFY24 to 4QFY24 and 3QFY25 respectively.
       Test and Evaluation: DBD Developmental Testing (DT) and Integrated Testing (IT) shifted from 3QFY25 to 4QFY25.
       Production Milestones: ALQ-214 Shop Replaceable Assembly (SRA) Retrofit contract awards and deliveries updated to align with procurement budget. DBD
       contract awards and deliveries updated to align with planned production option award and delivery dates.

       Project Unit 3308/Technology Development: N/A

       Project Unit 3309/Assault Survivability Optimization: Schedule updated to reflect CC, iASE and Advanced Radio Frequency Countermeasure (RFCM) schedule
       changes.

       The following CC milestones were changed due to required scope and schedule increase to OTA to address system security and F/A-18 vibration requirements.
       DT/Test Readiness Review (TRR) 4QFY25 to 3QFY26, EMD Test Asset Delivery 3QFY24 to 4QFY25 and, Power PC Operational Flight Program (OFP)/Mission
       Data File (MDF) End 3QFY24 to 2QFY26. Consolidated F/A-18/MH-60 Multi-Spectral Defense Electronic Warfare System Support Activity (MDEWSSA)/SW
       Integration Lab/DT/Maintenance Demonstration (MDemo) to DT/Operational Assessment (OA) events begin 3QFY26. Consolidated P-8/CMV-22 MDEWSSA/
       MDemo/DT to DT/Operational Test (OT) event begins 4QFY26. In order to buy back schedule time, program separated CC Sequencer and Dispenser
       Preliminary Design Review (PDR) and Critical Design Review (CDR). CC Sequencer PDR was completed 4QFY23. CC Dispenser PDR was completed 1QFY25.
       CC Sequencer CDR was completed 4QFY24 and Dispenser CDR is now scheduled 4QFY25.


