component reliability and onboard systems performance as well as approved product improvements of the VH-92A; Mission Communications System upgrades and avionics
systems; extended range cabin noise reduction, cabin upgrades, and Power Margin Inc 1 consisting of vehicle performance enhancements, high hot performance, transient
torque.

