FY 2026 increased compared to FY 2025 by $4.969 million due to a transfer of effort from Program Element 0602201F,
Aerospace Vehicle Technologies, Project 625172 Nuclear System Technology, in order to enhance transparency and traceability
of the nuclear Science & Technology portfolio.
